# 👥 Employee & Team Manager Dashboard Wireframes

## 💻 Desktop View
These dashboards are designed to support both employees and team managers with clear visibility, task management, and performance tracking.

### 🔹 Key Sections
- 🧭 Navigation: Dashboard, Profile/Team, Tasks, Reports, Settings  
- 📈 Overview: Tasks summary, performance metrics, pending actions  
- 📋 Task Management: View, update, assign, and track tasks  
- 👥 Team / Profile: Employee details or team member management  
- 📊 Reports: Performance insights and productivity tracking  
- 🔔 Notifications: Alerts for updates, approvals, and deadlines  

---

## 📱 Mobile View
Optimized for quick access and ease of use on mobile devices.

### 🔹 Key Sections
- ☰ Collapsible menu for navigation  
- 📊 Summary cards (tasks, performance, updates)  
- 📋 Task list (scrollable with quick actions)  
- 👥 Team/Employee view  
- 🔔 Real-time notifications  
- ➕ Quick actions (update task, assign task, approvals)  

---

## 🧠 Design Approach
- Low-fidelity (Lo-Fi) wireframes  
- Focus on simple navigation and user flow  
- Responsive design (Desktop + Mobile)  
- Minimal styling (grayscale, placeholders)  

